import { Button, Card, CardContent, Typography, styled } from '@mui/material'
import React from 'react'

const TrignleImg = styled("img")({
    right: 0,
    bottom: 0,
    height: 170,
    position: "absolute"
})

const TrophyImg = styled("img")({
    right: 36,
    bottom: 20,
    height: 98,
    position: 'absolute'
})

const Achivement = () => {
    return (
        <Card className='' sx={{position:"relative"}}>
            <CardContent>
                <Typography variant='h6' sx={{letterSpacing:".25px"}}>
                    Book Store
                </Typography>
                <Typography variant='body2'>Congratulations ðŸ¥³ </Typography>
                <Typography variant='h5' sx={{my:3.1}}> 420.8k </Typography>

                <Button size='small' variant='contained'>View Sales</Button>

                <TrignleImg src=''></TrignleImg>
                <TrophyImg src='https://ecommerce-codewithzosh.vercel.app/images/misc/trophy.png'/>
            </CardContent>
        </Card>
    )
}

export default Achivement
